juga tak memahami peraturannya.

7
00:01:51,129 --> 00:01:52,410
Agaknya ini bakat.

8
00:01:53,330 --> 00:01:54,169
Kalau ada masa kelak,

9
00:01:54,690 --> 00:01:56,889
saya pasti akan pergi ke Istana Qing Chi
dan minta tunjuk ajar.

10
00:01:57,650 --> 00:01:58,090
Baik.

11
00:01:59,249 --> 00:02:00,050
Baguslah begini.

12
00:02:02,290 --> 00:02:03,970
Tadi, awak bukan sengaja
bagi saya memang?

13
00:02:05,730 --> 00:02:06,449
Tak mungkin.

14
00:02:07,129 --> 00:02:07,889
Saya dah minum teh

15
00:02:08,050 --> 00:02:08,769
dan main catur.

16
00:02:08,970 --> 00:02:09,970
Saya perlu balik ke Istana Syurga.

17
00:02:10,129 --> 00:02:10,650
Ya.

18
00:02:10,930 --> 00:02:12,050
Masa memang tak awal lagi.

19
00:02:13,489 --> 00:02:15,450
Apa kata awak balik
setelah habis makan malam?

20
00:02:16,209 --> 00:02:18,170
Setelah makan malam, awak nak kata,

21
00:02:18,329 --> 00:02:19,010
dah lewat ini,

22
00:02:19,129 --> 00:02:20,769
apa kata bermalam di khemah awak?

23
00:02:22,569 --> 00:02:23,530
Mengapa awak fikir begini?

24
00:02:24,129 --> 00:02:26,329
Inilah jalan cerita persembahan
di atas pentas.

25
00:02:26,969 --> 00:02:27,930
Saya tak pernah menyaksikan persembahan.

26
00:02:28,930 --> 00:02:30,329
Saya bawa awak pergi ke Alam Manusia
kalau kita ada masa.

27
00:02:31,090 --> 00:02:31,650
Baik.

28
00:02:33,569 --> 00:02:34,569
Saya memang nak balik.

29
00:02:34,569 --> 00:02:35,730
Entah Hou Chi dan Qing Mu

30
00:02:35,730 --> 00:02:36,930
berjaya ambil Mutiara Kumpul Rohani.

31
00:02:37,329 --> 00:02:38,530
Saya risau akan hal ini.

32
00:02:40,090 --> 00:02:40,569
Baik.

33
00:02:40,569 --> 00:02:41,530
Maklum!

34
00:02:43,129 --> 00:02:43,730
Putera ngah,

35
00:02:43,930 --> 00:02:45,209
Maharaja Syaitan mengiringi
pasukan tentera untuk berperang.

36
00:02:45,409 --> 00:02:47,170
Dia kata nak jumpa putera ngah
dan Betari Feng Ran.

37
00:02:48,609 --> 00:02:49,890
Mengapa dia tahu saya berada di sini?

38
00:02:49,890 --> 00:02:51,689
Awak perlu terima kenyataan ini.

39
00:02:52,209 --> 00:02:53,010
Awak dah agak

40
00:02:53,010 --> 00:02:54,010
dan sengaja mempertahankan saya?

41
00:02:54,530 --> 00:02:55,930
Awak dah ambil barang sihir
Puak Syaitan,

42
00:02:56,250 --> 00:02:58,290
mereka takkan biarkan hal ini.

43
00:02:59,530 --> 00:03:01,370
Namun, saya berada di sisi awak,

44
00:03:02,250 --> 00:03:03,329
saya pasti akan melindungi awak.

45
00:04:00,290 --> 00:04:01,049
Saya dah berikan perintah
kepada Istana Syurga.

46
00:04:01,730 --> 00:04:03,329
Askar dan panglima Istana Syurga
akan berikan bantuan.

47
00:04:03,530 --> 00:04:04,129
Maharaja Syaitan,

48
00:04:04,689 --> 00:04:05,849
awak memang nak berperang?

49
00:04:06,689 --> 00:04:08,409
Asalkan awak serahkan
Panji Kumpul Syaitan,

50
00:04:08,689 --> 00:04:10,930
saya pasti akan beredar.

51
00:04:11,329 --> 00:04:11,930
Maharaja Syaitan,

52
00:04:12,250 --> 00:04:13,930
Dewa Zi Han tak beritahu tuanku?

53
00:04:15,010 --> 00:04:15,730
Apa dia?

54
00:04:16,090 --> 00:04:17,930
Dia yang pinjamkan Panji Kumpul Syaitan
kepada Istana Qing Chi.

55
00:04:18,609 --> 00:04:19,409
Lucunya.

56
00:04:20,290 --> 00:04:21,730
Panji itu barang sihir puak kami,

57
00:04:22,090 --> 00:04:23,009
tak boleh pinjam kepada orang lain.

58
00:04:23,810 --> 00:04:24,769
Tuanku boleh tahan dia
kalau tak percaya.

59
00:04:25,209 --> 00:04:26,690
Mengapa awak tak balik ke
Istana Qing Chi,

60
00:04:27,250 --> 00:04:28,530
tapi pergi ke khemah Jing Jian

61
00:04:29,090 --> 00:04:30,810
selama empat jam?

62
00:04:32,609 --> 00:04:33,449
Apa kaitan dengan awak?

63
00:04:34,650 --> 00:04:35,690
Feng Ran kawan lama saya.

64
00:04:36,289 --> 00:04:37,489
Kami minum teh dan main catur,

65
00:04:37,810 --> 00:04:38,690
tak berkaitan dengan
Panji Kumpul Syaitan.

66
00:04:39,090 --> 00:04:40,130
Mengapa nak jelaskan kepada mereka?

67
00:04:42,250 --> 00:04:42,970
Maharaja Syaitan,

68
00:04:43,650 --> 00:04:45,530
Istana Qing Chi pinjam Panji
Kumpul Syaitan untuk selamatkan orang.

69
00:04:45,889 --> 00:04:47,930
Dewa Syaitan yang baik hati.

70
00:04:48,329 --> 00:04:49,009
Awak boleh hantar utusan bulu

71
00:04:49,130 --> 00:04:50,650
kepada dia kalau tak percaya.

72
00:04:52,769 --> 00:04:53,489
Putera ngah,

73
00:04:54,130 --> 00:04:55,130
Puak Syaitan lebih lemah
daripada Puak Betara

74
00:04:55,570 --> 00:04:57,169
selama ini.

75
00:04:57,530 --> 00:04:58,850
Kita selalu ditindas.

76
00:04:59,370 --> 00:05:01,250
Dewa Syaitan dah sedarkan diri,

77
00:05:02,049 --> 00:05:04,449
saya ingat kita boleh
mengetuai tiga alam.

78
00:05:04,850 --> 00:05:05,810
Tak sangka

79
00:05:06,250 --> 00:05:08,410
tentera berjuang bermati-matian
di medan perang,

80
00:05:08,729 --> 00:05:09,850
Dewa Syaitan pula

81
00:05:09,850 --> 00:05:12,850
selalu tolong Hou Chi
dari Istana Qing Chi.

82
00:05:13,130 --> 00:05:14,410
Sekarang, dia serahkan
Panji Kumpul Syaitan

83
00:05:14,410 --> 00:05:16,329
kepada dia dan minta
Feng Ran bawa pergi.

84
00:05:17,130 --> 00:05:18,410
Kalau teruskan begini,

85
00:05:19,090 --> 00:05:20,250
Puak Betara belum menyerang kita,

86
00:05:20,570 --> 00:05:21,930
tapi Puak Syaitan dah terancam.

87
00:05:22,329 --> 00:05:22,930
Diam!

88
00:05:24,449 --> 00:05:25,769
Dia Dewa Syaitan,

89
00:05:26,209 --> 00:05:27,530
dewa kepada Puak Syaitan.

90
00:05:27,850 --> 00:05:29,489
Siapa suruh awak cakap begini?

91
00:05:29,650 --> 00:05:30,289
Dewa Bapa.

92
00:05:31,609 --> 00:05:32,810
Hal ini tak boleh biarkan saja.

93
00:05:33,609 --> 00:05:35,049
Tak apa kita tak campur tangan
dalam isu Istana Qing Chi.

94
00:05:36,009 --> 00:05:37,250
Sekarang, peperangan amat serius.

95
00:05:37,810 --> 00:05:38,609
Habislah kalau

96
00:05:39,130 --> 00:05:40,530
Panji Kumpul Syaitan jatuh
ke dalam tangan Istana Syurga.

97
00:05:42,090 --> 00:05:43,889
Biar Istana Qing Chi pinjam daripada
Dewa Agung pun,

98
00:05:44,850 --> 00:05:45,889
dah empat jam berlalu.

99
00:05:46,410 --> 00:05:47,489
Mereka patut pulangkan panji!

100
00:05:47,690 --> 00:05:48,970
Panji Kumpul Syaitan
tiada dalam tangan saya.

101
00:05:48,970 --> 00:05:49,889
Saya dah serahkan kepada Hou Chi.

102
00:05:50,289 --> 00:05:52,209
Kalau mampu, kamu boleh
ambil dari Istana Syurga.

103
00:05:57,370 --> 00:05:57,930
Susunkan pasukan!

104
00:05:58,090 --> 00:05:58,889
Melindungi putera ngah!

105
00:06:10,289 --> 00:06:11,049
Mengapa boleh begini?

106
00:06:11,650 --> 00:06:13,970
Bukankah kuasa jahat dimeterai
di Istana Bawah Tanah?

107
00:06:14,410 --> 00:06:15,370
Kita dah sampai lewat.

108
00:06:15,850 --> 00:06:16,410
Saya yang bersalah.

109
00:06:16,889 --> 00:06:17,970
Hari itu, saya terlalu cuai

110
00:06:18,250 --> 00:06:19,169
dan ambil Menara Tahan Roh pergi.

111
00:06:19,810 --> 00:06:21,289
Bi Xi dan Wu Huan dah berpakat,

112
00:06:21,289 --> 00:06:21,970
bukan salah awak.

113
00:06:22,970 --> 00:06:23,889
Saya yang bersalah.

114
00:06:24,370 --> 00:06:25,209
Demi selamatkan Bo Xuan,

115
00:06:25,609 --> 00:06:26,810
saya dah menyusahkan Alam Manusia.

116
00:06:27,289 --> 00:06:29,410
Hari ini, biar habiskan
tahap kuasa saya pun,

117
00:06:30,049 --> 00:06:30,970
saya mahu menolak balik

118
00:06:30,970 --> 00:06:32,250
kuasa jahat ke dalam Istana Bawah Tanah.

119
00:06:32,970 --> 00:06:33,970
Saya dah dirikan sekatan
dengan kuasa rohani

120
00:06:34,090 --> 00:06:35,250
di kawasan paling tinggi
di makam diraja

121
00:06:35,729 --> 00:06:37,690
untuk mengurung kuasa jahat
yang melimpah.

122
00:06:38,329 --> 00:06:39,489
Awak bahagikan sekatan itu

123
00:06:39,930 --> 00:06:41,329
untuk hapuskan kuasa jahat!

124
00:06:41,690 --> 00:06:43,250
Baik. Kita bekerjasama.

125
00:07:06,370 --> 00:07:08,370
(Alamak. Kuasa rohani rantai tangan
tak berkesan.)

126
00:07:08,729 --> 00:07:09,530
(Berdasarkan kuasa rohani saya,)

127
00:07:09,810 --> 00:07:11,169
(saya takut tak boleh mengukuhkan
sekatan ini.)

128
00:07:19,882 --> 00:07:22,042
Hou Chi, awak tak nak hidup lagi?

129
00:07:22,762 --> 00:07:23,482
Tak perlu awak pedulikan saya!

130
00:07:23,602 --> 00:07:24,563
Cepat menyucikan kuasa jahat!

131
00:07:26,720 --> 00:07:27,359
Feng Ran,

132
00:07:28,070 --> 00:07:30,871
saya hormati Dewa Gu Jun
dan Dewi Hou Chi,

133
00:07:31,230 --> 00:07:32,591
jadi, saya layan awak dengan baik.

134
00:07:33,270 --> 00:07:34,631
Kalau awak tak reti hargai,

135
00:07:35,351 --> 00:07:39,670
hari ini, saya nak
berhitung dengan awak.

136
00:07:49,359 --> 00:07:49,840
Abang long,

137
00:07:49,840 --> 00:07:50,639
mengapa baru sampai?

138
00:07:50,919 --> 00:07:51,679
Ini kecemasan,

139
00:07:52,000 --> 00:07:52,919
abang long ditahan dalam perjalanan.

140
00:08:03,639 --> 00:08:04,359
Feng Ran.

141
00:08:05,250 --> 00:08:05,930
Dewa Gu Jun.

142
00:08:06,250 --> 00:08:09,090
Baru saya menyucikan kuasa jahat
di kawasan ini,

143
00:08:09,729 --> 00:08:10,769
tapi peperangan hampir tercetus.

144
00:08:13,130 --> 00:08:13,850
Sen Jian,

145
00:08:14,329 --> 00:08:15,530
awak pernah mengadu,

146
00:08:15,850 --> 00:08:17,650
Puak Betara menindas Puak Syaitan.

147
00:08:18,049 --> 00:08:18,930
Hari ini,

148
00:08:19,690 --> 00:08:21,769
awak mahu puak syaitan berperang dengan

149
00:08:22,250 --> 00:08:23,169
Puak Betara

150
00:08:23,609 --> 00:08:25,329
sampai kedua-dua puak dalam kesusahan?

151
00:08:26,690 --> 00:08:28,850
Feng Ran dah curi
Panji Kumpul Syaitan kami

152
00:08:29,329 --> 00:08:30,850
dan bergaul rapat dengan Jing Jian.

153
00:08:31,289 --> 00:08:33,009
Saya risau, Panji Kumpul Syaitan akan
jatuh ke dalam Istana Syurga

154
00:08:33,410 --> 00:08:34,650
dan membawa keburukan kepada
Puak Syaitan.

155
00:08:35,009 --> 00:08:36,889
Jadi, saya mahukan penjelasan.

156
00:08:39,010 --> 00:08:39,930
Biar betul?

157
00:08:40,489 --> 00:08:41,609
Kesedaran rohani Bo Xuan
semakin lemah.

158
00:08:41,849 --> 00:08:43,130
Panji Kumpul Syaitan
boleh selamatkan dia.

159
00:08:43,370 --> 00:08:45,289
Dewa Syaitan yang pinjamkan Panji
Kumpul Syaitan kepada Istana Qing Chi.

160
00:08:45,969 --> 00:08:47,130
Panji Kumpul Syaitan tak cukup

161
00:08:47,649 --> 00:08:49,570
untuk kumpulkan kesedaran rohani.

162
00:08:49,770 --> 00:08:50,930
Apa lagi yang Hou Chi ambil?

163
00:08:51,529 --> 00:08:53,330
Mutiara Kumpul Rohani
dan Menara Tahan Roh.

164
00:08:53,770 --> 00:08:54,729
Di mana dia?

165
00:08:55,049 --> 00:08:55,649
Istana Syurga.

166
00:08:59,289 --> 00:09:00,729
Saya dah faham hal ini.

167
00:09:01,330 --> 00:09:01,930
Sen Jian,

168
00:09:02,250 --> 00:09:03,570
awak balik ke Istana Xuan Jing.

169
00:09:03,770 --> 00:09:04,330
Lain kali,

170
00:09:04,450 --> 00:09:06,089
saya akan jelaskan hal ini kepada awak.

171
00:09:06,489 --> 00:09:07,010
Ya.

172
00:09:08,810 --> 00:09:11,169
Hari ini, saya berikan muka
kepada Istana Qing Chi.

173
00:09:11,890 --> 00:09:12,450
Beredar!

174
00:09:17,370 --> 00:09:19,250
Terima kasih atas bantuan Dewa Gu Jun.

175
00:09:21,250 --> 00:09:22,969
Disebabkan dia.

176
00:09:24,729 --> 00:09:25,250
Jing Jian.

177
00:09:26,089 --> 00:09:27,609
Awak masih nak bersama dengan dia?

178
00:09:27,609 --> 00:09:28,210
Abang long.

179
00:09:29,969 --> 00:09:31,609
Jing Yang nak maklumkan hal ini
kepada Raja Syurga di Istana Syurga.

180
00:09:32,210 --> 00:09:32,890
Minta diri dulu.

181
00:09:33,330 --> 00:09:33,810
Tunggu sebentar.

182
00:09:34,890 --> 00:09:36,570
Istana Qing Chi
yang mengakibatkan hal ini.

183
00:09:36,969 --> 00:09:38,450
Saya ikut awak balik ke Istana Syurga.

184
00:09:40,489 --> 00:09:41,010
Kenapa?

185
00:09:41,609 --> 00:09:42,690
Saya tak boleh pergi?

186
00:09:44,370 --> 00:09:45,250
Kalau begini,

187
00:09:45,570 --> 00:09:46,130
dewa,

188
00:09:47,169 --> 00:09:47,690
dipersilakan.

189
00:10:21,250 --> 00:10:21,770
Qing Mu.

190
00:10:24,130 --> 00:10:24,849
Bagaimana dengan awak?

191
00:10:25,489 --> 00:10:26,130
Saya tak apa-apa.

192
00:10:26,930 --> 00:10:28,570
Kuasa jahat merasuk jasad awak,
mustahil tak apa-apa.

193
00:10:29,609 --> 00:10:31,049
Entah bila kuasa jahat ini terbocor.

194
00:10:31,489 --> 00:10:32,930
Mungkin dah tersebar di Alam Manusia.

195
00:10:33,609 --> 00:10:34,690
Saya akan memeterai kuasa jahat

196
00:10:34,690 --> 00:10:36,049
yang merasuk jasad saya ke dalam
Istana Bawah Tanah

197
00:10:36,489 --> 00:10:38,010
agar boleh ringankan kesalahan awak.

198
00:10:38,489 --> 00:10:39,130
Kelak...

199
00:10:40,810 --> 00:10:41,370
Saya tak apa-apa.

200
00:10:43,609 --> 00:10:44,330
Awak mempercayai saya.

201
00:10:45,370 --> 00:10:46,250
Adanya bantuan Kuasa Tai Chang,

202
00:10:46,690 --> 00:10:48,010
saya boleh menahan kuasa jahat
di dalam badan saya,

203
00:10:48,370 --> 00:10:49,250
takkan mencederakan nadi rohani.

204
00:10:50,250 --> 00:10:51,010
Jangan awak menipu.

205
00:10:51,250 --> 00:10:52,969
Saya tak nak kehilangan siapa-siapa pun.

206
00:10:53,770 --> 00:10:55,169
Pernahkah saya menipu awak?

207
00:10:55,690 --> 00:10:56,969
Petir Jiu Chong di Altar Qing Long

208
00:10:56,969 --> 00:10:57,729
tak dapat menyambar saya,

209
