apatah lagi kuasa jahat
di Alam Manusia.

210
00:11:00,169 --> 00:11:01,890
Awak dah pandang rendah terhadap
betara atasan pertama di Puak Betara.

211
00:11:02,570 --> 00:11:03,330
Awak pergi ke Istana Syurga

212
00:11:03,690 --> 00:11:05,570
dan maklumkan Raja Syurga,
memeterai kuasa jahat dah pecah.

213
00:11:06,330 --> 00:11:07,849
Saya akan pergi jumpa awak
setelah memeterai kuasa jahat.

214
00:11:08,570 --> 00:11:09,890
Biar saya pergi memeterai kuasa jahat,

215
00:11:09,969 --> 00:11:11,049
awak maklumkan Raja Syurga.

216
00:11:11,210 --> 00:11:12,010
Dungu.

217
00:11:12,210 --> 00:11:13,130
Kuasa jahat ada dalam badan saya,

218
00:11:13,330 --> 00:11:14,489
awak nak memeterai saya?

219
00:11:17,450 --> 00:11:17,930
Cepat,

220
00:11:18,089 --> 00:11:18,810
tiada masa lagi.

221
00:11:19,089 --> 00:11:20,690
Kita perlu balik ke Istana Qing Chi
untuk selamatkan Bo Xuan.

222
00:11:21,690 --> 00:11:22,570
Jangan awak tercedera lagi.

223
00:11:23,729 --> 00:11:24,770
Kita berjumpa di Istana Syurga.

224
00:11:28,890 --> 00:11:29,489
Hou Chi.

225
00:11:31,210 --> 00:11:33,450
Saya dah kenal pasti awaklah orang itu
sejak di Altar Qing Long.

226
00:11:34,089 --> 00:11:35,370
Kelak, tak kira apa yang berlaku pun,

227
00:11:35,729 --> 00:11:36,969
saya akan menemani awak.

228
00:11:37,810 --> 00:11:38,770
Saya yang menyusahkan awak

229
